        </div>
        <div class="pub-item">
          <div class="pub-meta">
            <h3>The invisible gold mines of Guanacaste: Territorial Fiscal Balance and real-estate extractivism in the district of Nosara</h3>
            <div class="pub-source">2026 - Academic article - OBTUR-UNA (Tourism Observatory, Universidad Nacional) - In Spanish</div>
            <p>Executive summary of the 123-page Territorial Fiscal Balance, published by the National University's Tourism Observatory. Frames Nosara as a case of systematic territorial wealth extraction through real estate and tourism, without proportional community reinvestment.</p>
