          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-item">
          <div class="pub-meta">
            <h3>Nosara: learning about data and narratives</h3>
            <div class="pub-source">2026 - Op-ed - Semanario Universidad - In Spanish</div>
            <p>A defense of the Territorial Fiscal Balance methodology: what a territory can measure, it can govern.</p>
            <a href="https://semanariouniversidad.com/opinion/nosara-aprender-sobre-datos-y-relatos/" class="pub-action" target="_blank">Read original (Spanish) <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="pub-item">
          <div class="pub-meta">
            <h3>Say "entrepreneurship" and a venture dies</h3>
            <div class="pub-source">2017 - Op-ed - La Republica - In Spanish</div>
            <p>A column on entrepreneurship culture, written as Project Coordinator at Yo Emprendedor.</p>
            <a href="https://www.larepublica.net/noticia/al-decir-emprendedurismo-un-emprendimiento-muere" class="pub-action" target="_blank">Read original (Spanish) <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg></a>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div style="margin-top: 1rem;"><a href="https://www.censonosara.com/blog" class="btn btn-outline" target="_blank">More articles on the blog</a></div>
      </section>

      <!-- PRESS -->
      <section class="pub-section">
        <div class="pub-section-head">
          <div class="pub-ico" style="background: var(--warm-50); color: var(--warm);"><svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M4 22h16a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V4a2 2 0 0 0-2-2H8a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 1-2 2zm0 0a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-9c0-1.1.9-2 2-2h2"/><path d="M18 14h-8"/><path d="M15 18h-5"/><path d="M10 6h8v4h-8V6z"/></svg></div>
