        </div>
        <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Nosara generates $1.9B a year and receives only $25k in direct investment</h3><div class="pub-source">2026 - Semanario Universidad - In Spanish</div><p>Lead coverage of the Territorial Fiscal Balance: a return of 0.62 cents for every colon Nosara generates.</p><a href="https://semanariouniversidad.com/pais/nosara-genera-%E2%82%A1958-000-millones-al-ano-y-solo-recibe-%E2%82%A112-millones-en-inversion-directa/" class="pub-action" target="_blank">Read original (Spanish) <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg></a></div></div>
        <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Guanacaste in English: Dollars and Luxury Inundate Costa Rica's Most Touristy Province</h3><div class="pub-source">2025 - El Faro - In English</div><p>Regional feature profiling me as the researcher who led the 2024 Nosara census.</p><a href="https://beta.elfaro.net/en/by-invitation/guanacaste-in-english-dollars-and-luxury-inundate-costa-ricas-most-touristy-province" class="pub-action" target="_blank">Read article <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg></a></div></div>
        <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Nosara presents its first district census and exposes urgent gaps</h3><div class="pub-source">2025 - CRHoy - In Spanish</div><p>Coverage of the census launch, citing me as coordinator and researcher.</p><a href="https://crhoy.com/nacionales/nosara-presenta-su-primer-censo-distrital-y-expone-cambios-brechas-y-desafios-urgentes/" class="pub-action" target="_blank">Read original (Spanish) <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg></a></div></div>
        <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>First community district census reveals strong imbalance in Nosara</h3><div class="pub-source">2025 - Delfino.cr - In Spanish</div><p>Results coverage, presented before the Nicoya Municipal Council.</p><a href="https://delfino.cr/2025/12/primer-censo-distrital-comunitario-revela-fuerte-desbalance-entre-crecimiento-y-capacidad-estatal-en-nosara" class="pub-action" target="_blank">Read original (Spanish) <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg></a></div></div>
        <div class="pub-item"><div class="pub-meta"><h3>Nosara Podcast: census, Vive el Sueno and Santa Marta ASADA</h3><div class="pub-source">2023 - Rich Burnam (Nosara Podcast) - In English</div><p>Long-form interview on Nosara's challenges and opportunities.</p><a href="https://richburnam.com/2023/02/10/emmanual-gutierrez-covers-nosara-crece-vive-el-sueno-santa-marta-asada-nosara-nicoya-relation-and-much-more-nosara-challenges-and-opportunities/" class="pub-action" target="_blank">Listen <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M18 13v6a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H5a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V8a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h6"/><polyline points="15 3 21 3 21 9"/><line x1="10" y1="14" x2="21" y2="3"/></svg></a></div></div>
      </section>

      <!-- RESEARCH IN PROGRESS -->
      <section class="pub-section">
        <div class="pub-section-head">
